cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reproduce or extend this work, please cite the IEEE Access manuscript and this reproducibility deposit."
title: "A Skill-Mediated LLM Workflow for Migrating a .NET Monolith to Microservices: Reproducibility Deposit"
abstract: >
  Companion deposit for the IEEE Access submission by Olariu and Alboaie.
  Contains ten Claude Code skill scripts, the PetRescue and eShopOnWeb
  case-study codebases tagged at the experimental commit, raw run logs
  and transcripts, the security injection corpus, the twenty-dimension
  scoring rubrics, the dependency-free scoring and inferential
  statistics scripts, the verifier changelog, and a full environment
  manifest.
type: dataset
authors:
